hypothetically speaking, she were a mature woman,

846
00:36:13,080 --> 00:36:14,760
she's not my type.

847
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:21,120
If you're still worried,

848
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,740
I can easily speak to Betty

849
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:24,520
and clear things up in front of you.

850
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,650
No, no, no. We can't handle it that way.

851
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:29,410
I need to figure something out.

852
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:34,120
Betty, this child,

853
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:37,540
although she seems carefree on the surface,

854
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:39,660
is actually very fragile inside.

855
00:36:41,040 --> 00:36:43,440
Because of the relationship between me and her father,

856
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:45,300
she finds it hard to trust others.

857
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:48,520
If you reject her,

858
00:36:48,520 --> 00:36:51,120
yes, her hopes would be cut off,

859
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:53,320
but I'm afraid she might not be able to cope

860
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,400
and do something foolish,

861
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:55,800
which would be terrible.

862
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:56,680
I understand.

863
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,520
Besides,

864
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:59,360
if this isn't handled properly,

865
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,800
when you two become step-siblings in the future,

866
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:04,520
wouldn't that be awkward, right?

867
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,200
Right.

868
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:10,760
Okay, meeting adjourned.

869
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:29,440
Oh, Mom.

870
00:37:31,240 --> 00:37:32,480
You look so tired,

871
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:33,600
are you about to go to bed?

872
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:35,600
Why are you calling at this hour?

873
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,360
I miss you.

874
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:40,720
We're about to go to bed.

875
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,880
Mom, is your shoulder still hurting?

876
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:46,040
Is that herbal patch I bought you working well?

877
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,080
It works quite well,

878
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,960
the pain is almost gone now.

879
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:51,160
Should I send you some more?

880
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:52,680
No need,

881
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:55,320
international shipping is too much trouble.

882
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:58,200
Then I'll just bring some back with me next time I visit.

883
00:37:58,200 --> 00:37:59,360
Are you kidding me?

884
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,000
Aren't you working anymore?

885
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:02,530
Why come back for no reason,

886
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:04,480
wasting money on plane tickets?

887
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:08,120
Mom, you've changed.

888
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:11,220
You used to be eager to pay for my ticket to come home.

889
00:38:14,720 --> 00:38:15,560
Mom,

890
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,360
what's wrong?

891
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:21,540
I've been busy with our family business lately,

892
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:24,100
your father and I are planning to go on a trip,

893
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:27,240
and there'd be no one to take care of you if you came back.

894
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:28,640
Where are you guys going?

895
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:31,120
We're going to your uncle's place.

896
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:32,520
Isn't Uncle in Hainan?

897
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:33,840
Yes,

898
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,760
we're going to Hainan.

899
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,010
Why are you visiting Uncle?

900
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:40,800
Haven't seen him for a while, just going for a visit.

901
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:42,400
Don't ask so many questions.

902
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,240
Mom,

903
00:38:44,560 --> 00:38:46,720
I've been in touch with Dahua recently,

904
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,180
my high school classmate.

905
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:50,320
Doesn't he run a construction company back home?

906
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:52,440
He wants me to join him.

907
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:54,600
I've been thinking,

908
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:57,600
the domestic market is good now,

909
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:58,720
so maybe,

910
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:01,640
maybe after I get my degree,

911
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:03,880
I could try developing my career back home.

912
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:06,240
That Dahua never tells the truth,

913
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:07,960
he's just a big talker.

914
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:10,900
Why come back when you have a good job in America?

915
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:14,840
Well, then,

916
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:18,400
I could go back to inherit the family business.

917
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:22,700
Why do you keep talking about coming back today?

918
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:25,240
You're not having problems in America, are you?

919
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:26,520
No,

920
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:27,880
it's just that over these years,

921
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,280
I've spent too little time with you both.

922
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:33,040
Besides, if something's happening at home,

923
00:39:33,040 --> 00:39:33,960
you don't tell me about it.

924
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:35,760
Shouldn't I come back and check?

925
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:38,640
What good would telling you do?

926
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,240
I could help share your burdens,

927
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:41,640
discuss things with you.

928
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:45,120
Mom,

929
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,520
has something happened at home?

930
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,000
Please don't hide anything from me.

931
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,200
It's nothing.

932
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:53,960
You know, in business,

933
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:56,160
there are times when cash flow gets tight.

934
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:57,280
If we ask your uncle,

935
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:59,600
we should be able to get through this.

936
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,840
Well, how about this,

937
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:03,320
wait until I come back to China,

938
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,360
we'll go see my uncle together.

939
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:05,640
I haven't seen him in ages.

940
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:06,360
No, no,

941
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:08,770
you just focus on your work in America.

942
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:10,960
Don't worry about family matters here.

943
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,880
Alright, alright,

944
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:13,040
okay, calm down,

945
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:14,240
what's the big deal?

946
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,840
Fine, I won't come back then.

947
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:18,760
You're our family's only hope.

948
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,930
Just focus on your work over there,

949
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:23,520
we can handle our problems ourselves.

950
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,800
Okay, got it.

951
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,600
Go to sleep now,

952
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:27,960
son. Bye-bye.

953
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,280
Hello, Uncle.

954
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:58,440
It's me, Guo Yang.

955
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,240
Did your mother ask you to call me?

956
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,320
No,

957
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:05,040
but didn't my mom say she's coming to see you in a few days?

958
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,720
It's been a long time since I called you,

959
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:07,760
just wanted to check in

960
00:41:07,760 --> 00:41:09,820
and see how you've been doing lately.

961
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,560
I've already helped with everything I can,

962
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:14,200
but the mess your family is in

963
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:16,080
isn't something I alone can fix.

964
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:19,760
Wait, Uncle, what do you mean by that?

965
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:22,900
It's my dad's business that's in trouble, isn't it?

966
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,720
At a time like this,

967
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,720
what's the point of keeping secrets anymore?

968
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,600
Anyway,

969
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:31,680
there's nothing I can do about your family's problems.

970
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,360
Tell your parents

971
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,280
not to come looking for us.

972
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,640
Our whole family won't be home,

973
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:37,080
so it would be a waste of their time.

974
00:41:37,080 --> 00:41:38,940
Uncle, how can you talk like that?

975
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:55,240
Honey, why aren't you in bed yet?

976
00:41:57,880 --> 00:41:58,680
What's wrong?

977
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:01,520
Something must have happened at home.

978
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,780
I just called my uncle,

979
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:05,400
he said he didn't know my mom was going to see him,

980
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:07,840
and that he couldn't help with whatever's happening in my family.

981
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:09,170
Have you asked your mom?

982
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:10,240
I talked to her,

983
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:12,400
but she won't tell me what's really going on.

984
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,530
Something's wrong.

985
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,840
What should we do?
